data.description: Welcome to your dream home! This beautiful, newly built 3 bedroom, 2.5 bathroom single family home is a true gem. Constructed in 2020, it boasts modern amenities and design, making it the perfect place to call home. Situated in a close-knit community, this residence offers a serene and welcoming atmosphere. As you step inside, you'll immediately appreciate the open concept layout. The kitchen, with its sleek countertops and stainless steel appliances, overlooks the spacious living room and dining area. This design is ideal for entertaining, as it allows you to seamlessly connect with your family and guests while preparing meals. On the main floor, you'll find a convenient half bath for guests, ensuring comfort and functionality. The downstairs living area is bright and inviting, creating a warm ambiance that welcomes you home each day. Upstairs, privacy and convenience are at their finest. The master suite occupies its own side of the house, providing a tranquil retreat for relaxation. This spacious master bedroom features a generously sized closet and an ensuite bathroom complete with an oversized soaking tub, a separate shower, and double sinks. Pamper yourself in luxury and style. On the opposite side of the upper floor, you'll discover two secondary bedrooms, perfect for family members or guests. A well-appointed hall bathroom and a dedicated laundry room make daily routines a breeze. Storage will never be an issue in this home, with ample closet space and cleverly designed storage solutions throughout. You'll have room for all your belongings without sacrificing aesthetics. The exterior of the house is equally impressive, with a nice backyard that offers opportunities for outdoor recreation and relaxation. Whether you're gardening, barbecuing, or simply enjoying the fresh air, this backyard space will become a cherished part of your home. Don't miss out on the opportunity to make this stunning home your own. With its modern design, thoughtful layout, and close-knit community, it's the perfect place to create lasting memories. Come and experience the lifestyle you've been dreaming of – schedule a viewing today!
